nodes.text: An unknown governor-general was installed over Corellia by the New Republic following the ouster of Thrackan Sal-Solo in 28 ABY, during the Yuuzhan Vong War.

Sometime after the end of the war in 29 ABY, the Galactic Alliance removed the governor-general from Corellia as a reward for the system supporting the Alliance's war effort. The position was replaced with that of Five World Prime Minister, of whom the first was Aidel Saxan.
